g.desc: The use of a factory method in combination with a product int...

g.text: The use of a factory method in combination with a product interface makes it easy to extend the system without modifying it. We can introduce ‘new constructors’ for our class, so it is not bounded to a specific implementation. Product creation is outsourced to our sub-type. Dependency inversion between product interface and creator, inheritance between creator and concrete creator realize OCP.
